 kWp. Med dagens kraftpris og nettleie vil det kunne redusere str\u00f8mregningen med 3-6000 kroner i \u00e5ret.", "H\u00f8ringsfristen for det nye forslaget er 10. oktober, og de nye reglene kan tidligst bli innf\u00f8rt 1. januar 2015."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e7bd86915366f5b342b42f315a6ed7408517ca917025c392b69a3395d61e4885"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T04:11:32.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Solceller p\u00e5 l\u00e5vetaket eller en vindm\u00f8lle p\u00e5 tunet kan krympe str\u00f8mregningen med flere tusenlapper. N\u00e5 skal det bli mer l\u00f8nnsomt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article9857296.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Solceller.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b70457f74c841fa67438102a5034fe81594bcd58.jpg?598c2000"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["N\u00e5 blir det billigere \u00e5 lage egen str\u00f8m -adressa.no", "Krever full nettleie", "L\u00e5vetaket kan v\u00e6re gull verdt"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b70457f74c841fa67438102a5034fe81594bcd58"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["str\u00f8m", "full nettleie", "produsere"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["slik nve", "norges", "s\u00f8r-norge", "sintef", "kwp"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/okonomi"]}, {"field": "og-image", "valu